          },
          "reviewBody": "A few days prior to the evening workshop Alan sent through a 2 page worksheet packing with useful information, which I found helpful. Alan also set the bracketing on my camera so I could compensate for the high contrast lighting.  Second review 8 January 2026 for 1:1 meeting on zoom This was a session to review edits on my photos for the LRPS, Alan was encouraging but also honest and what I needed to do to in order to progress my panel photos.",
