          },
          "reviewBody": "The service and expertise is outstanding. No hesitation in recommending his services. We worked together on my photography panel for a distinction qualification with the RPS. In all areas (art craft and science) he is a true expert. In addition his character is friendly and helpful. His knowledge is extensive and constantly growing. He supports all levels of photographers.  In addition to his support, I worked with him in the field planning and photographing a number of sites, on the coast, over 3 days. Once again a superb service. Peter",
