            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Mary Hamilton"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I chose Alan Ranger for photography processing instruction because he produces images of exceptional quality.  I was pleasantly surprised to discover that Alan is an outstanding teacher.  Alan explains how I could improve my images, then demonstrates several methods of enhancement.  I can recommend Alan's course to any photographer who wishes to optimise their image processing workflow.",
